00062 void BlockCompressionCodecLzo::deflate(const DynamicBuffer &input, DynamicBuffer &output, BlockCompressionHeader &header, size_t reserve) {
00063   uint32_t avail_out = (input.fill() + input.fill() / 16 + 64 + 3 + 4);
00064   int ret;
00065   lzo_uint out_len = avail_out;
00066   uint8_t *fence_ptr = 0;
00067 
00068   output.clear();
00069   output.reserve(header.length() + avail_out + reserve);
00070 
00071   fence_ptr = output.base + header.length() + (avail_out-4);
00072   memcpy(fence_ptr, fence_marker, 4);
00073 
00074   ret = lzo1x_1_compress(input.base, input.fill(), output.base+header.length(), &out_len, m_workmem);
00075   assert(ret == LZO_E_OK);
00076 
00077   /* check for an incompressible block */
00078   if (out_len >= input.fill()) {
00079     header.set_compression_type(NONE);
00080     memcpy(output.base+header.length(), input.base, input.fill());
00081     header.set_data_length(input.fill());
00082     header.set_data_zlength(input.fill());
00083   }
00084   else {
00085     header.set_compression_type(LZO);
00086     header.set_data_length(input.fill());
00087     header.set_data_zlength(out_len);
00088   }
00089   header.set_data_checksum(fletcher32(output.base + header.length(), header.get_data_zlength()));
00090 
00091   output.ptr = output.base;
00092   header.encode(&output.ptr);
00093   output.ptr += header.get_data_zlength();
00094 
00095   HT_EXPECT(!memcmp(fence_ptr, fence_marker, 4), Error::FAILED_EXPECTATION);
00096   HT_EXPECT(!memcmp(&m_workmem[LZO1X_1_MEM_COMPRESS], fence_marker, 4), Error::FAILED_EXPECTATION);
00097 }

00103 void BlockCompressionCodecLzo::inflate(const DynamicBuffer &input, DynamicBuffer &output, BlockCompressionHeader &header) {
00104   int ret;
00105   const uint8_t *msg_ptr = input.base;
00106   size_t remaining = input.fill();
00107   lzo_uint new_len;
00108 
00109   header.decode(&msg_ptr, &remaining);
00110 
00111   if (header.get_data_zlength() != remaining) {
00112     HT_ERRORF("Block decompression error, header zlength = %d, actual = %d", header.get_data_zlength(), remaining);
00113     HT_THROW(Error::BLOCK_COMPRESSOR_BAD_HEADER, "");
00114   }
00115 
00116   uint32_t checksum = fletcher32(msg_ptr, remaining);
00117   if (checksum != header.get_data_checksum()) {
00118     HT_ERRORF("Compressed block checksum mismatch header=%d, computed=%d", header.get_data_checksum(), checksum);
00119     HT_THROW(Error::BLOCK_COMPRESSOR_CHECKSUM_MISMATCH, "");
00120   }
00121 
00122   output.reserve(header.get_data_length());
00123 
00124    // check compress bit
00125   if (header.get_compression_type() == NONE)
00126     memcpy(output.base, msg_ptr, header.get_data_length());
00127   else {
00128     new_len = header.get_data_length();
00129     ret = lzo1x_decompress(msg_ptr, header.get_data_zlength(), output.base, &new_len, 0);
00130     if (ret != LZO_E_OK || new_len != header.get_data_length()) {
00131       HT_ERRORF("Lzo decompression error, rval = %d", ret);
00132       HT_THROW(Error::BLOCK_COMPRESSOR_INFLATE_ERROR, "");
00133     }
00134   }
00135   output.ptr = output.base + header.get_data_length();
00136 }
